  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Declaration">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[struct WindowInfoWin32 : public IFrameBuffer::WindowInfoBase;]]></Code>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>WindowInfoWin32</TypeRef> structure describes a Win32 window for <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.IFrameBuffer.BindWindow">IFrameBuffer.BindWindow</PageRef>.
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
      Availability: Windows when <TypeRef>COBALT_RENDERER_WIN32_SUPPORT</TypeRef> is enabled. This is automatically enabled on Windows unless platform binding selection is manual.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Members">
    <DataMemberList>
      <DataMemberListEntry Visibility="Public" Type="HINSTANCE" Name="instanceHandle">
        The Win32 application instance handle, or <TypeRef>nullptr</TypeRef> when not supplied.
      </DataMemberListEntry>
      <DataMemberListEntry Visibility="Public" Type="HWND" Name="windowHandle">
        The Win32 window handle.
      </DataMemberListEntry>
      <DataMemberListEntry Visibility="Public" Type="V2UInt32" Name="windowSizeInPixels">
        The drawable window size in pixels.
      </DataMemberListEntry>
    </DataMemberList>
  </Section>
